PATTERN RULES:
- Drop vowels whr possbl: "create"â†’"crt", "system"â†’"sys", "provide"â†’"prov"
- Use numbrs 4 words: "to"â†’"2", "for"â†’"4", "ate"â†’"8"
- Symbols 4 cmmn words: "&"="and", "@"="at", "w/"="with"
- -ingâ†’-ng: "doing"â†’"dong", "making"â†’"mkng", "creating"â†’"crtng"
- -tionâ†’-tn: "creation"â†’"cretn", "evaluation"â†’"evalutn"
